How much does it cost to travel in Mauritania

If you ever visit Mauritania, this prayer might always stay in your mind because sadly it’s going to be very expensive. Items such as visa, airfare, tarifs and tipping are usually expansive.

Expect to pay EUR 40 for 6 litre bottle of water. EUR 6 for a jar of prune, EUR 80 for flight to Nouad
